CrazyChess.pieces

Class AbstractPiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • CrazyChess.pieces.AbstractPiece
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bishop, BlankPiece, HazardPiece, King, Knight, Pawn, Powerup, Queen, Rook

    public abstract class AbstractPiece
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is the abstract class for all of the other classes of pieces. All other pieces extend this.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
